Name: Dashie's Puh-ranormal Activity
About the game: Dashie's Puh-ranormal Activity is a 3D first-person comedy/horror game developed for the YouTuber Dashie. (YouTube: DashieGames, DashieXP, DashieXP2). The game features various references to Dashie's skits and videos. In this game, Dashie is being haunted by the ghost of his ex and many of his past skit characters. You must find a way to escape and survive. Features: Multiple Enemies Multiple Sections Lots of jump scares Many references to Dashie's skits and videos Humor The game is not yet complete. This is an Early Access build that will give you access to the first, second and third level. 5 additional levels will be released at a later date.
